metadata.description:
Human life reminds me of the circle we walk in, leaving different marks on it: big or small, good or bad. Every circle here is someone's life story.

Explanation of some features:

    "Colors Mode": Hard => more emotional person, Light => less emotional person;
    "Palette" : characterizes the emotional state of the person (dark colors => bad actions, light colors => good actions);
    "Number of Marks": the number of important actions of the person that significantly affected her life;
    "Algo/Lifestyle": dynamics of a person's life; 
    "Activity Level": level of activity of the person during life (active, passive, etc.);
    "Lifetime": life expectancy (short, average, long).

Press "s" key in live mode to save current image, press "4" or "6" or "8" key to save bigger image.
